NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::ProveRdeps - Add release test to run 'prove'
    on distributions that depend on us

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::Test::ProveRdeps (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Test-ProveRdeps), released on 2020-01-30.

DESCRIPTION
    EXPERIMENTAL.

    This plugin adds the following files:

      xt/release/prove-rdeps.t

    This test script uses Test::ProveRdeps to check distributions depending
    on your distribution.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Dist-Zilla-Plugin-Test-ProveRdeps>.

SOURCE
